      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was humming at a low pitch earlier today and the wind literally stopped blowing for a second. i think i can actually influence the atmospheric pressure with specific tones. if there is a massive storm system coming in, what kind of frequency would i need to hit to stabilize the air and stop the pressure from dropping so fast?",
